Package Model

Class Movie

java.lang.Object
Model.Movie
public class Movie extends Object
This Movie Class is for: 1) Cinema Staff to Create(new Movie object) / Update(set) / Remove(set Showing status to ENDOFSHOWING) movies 2) Movie-goer user class to access(get) movie properties 3) Ticket class to access(get) movie properties
Since:
12/11/2022
